To track the changes

git --version
git init
git status
git add content.html
git add index.html
git commit -m "Initial commit"
git log

with the github

git remote add origin https://github.com/sruthi1729/firstone.git
git push -u origin master

to add files all at once we use
--git add .

git clone https://github.com/sruthi1729/firstone.git



git pull

